  <description><![CDATA[<p>The Hotel Villa Maria consists of two buildings set in spacious grounds. The rooms, reception and lounge are in the newer building while the restaurant and bar are located in the lovely old villa just opposite. Garden villas are set in the same grounds with quiet and beautiful gardens extending over 15,000m². The centre of Desenzano is approximately 30 minutes' walk away or a short ride on the bus which stops close to the hotel. A wide range of facilities are on offer including large outdoor swimming pool, extensive gardens with sunbathing terraces and sunloungers, tennis courts, restaurant and bar with outdoor terrace.</p>]]></description>
